# .trivyignore — Trivy CVE suppression list
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add CVE IDs here to suppress false positives that have been reviewed and
# accepted by the security team.
#
# Format: one CVE-ID per line, optionally with a comment.
# Suppression requires documented review in SECURITY_DECISIONS.md.
#
# Example:
# CVE-2023-XXXXX  # Reviewed YYYY-MM-DD: not exploitable in our config
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (No suppressions currently — all CVEs must be resolved.)
